# Copy to `.env` beside docker-compose.yml (Compose loads `.env` automatically).
# `.env` is gitignored.

# Host folder → /mnt/d/Photos inside the `webui` container (New Run / scope paths).
# - Docker CLI in WSL: default in compose is /mnt/d/Photos; often no `.env` needed.
# - Docker Desktop for Windows: set this to your Windows path or the bind will not see your files.
# PHOTOS_BIND_SOURCE=D:/Photos
